{{cquote|這將Venel Atelinas給予了提尼亞（Tin）的兒子{{efn|即[[卡斯托耳和波鲁克斯|卡斯托耳和波鲁克斯]]}}<ref name=TDT>{{cite book|title=The Etruscan language: an introduction |author1=Giuliano Bonfante |author2= Larissa Bonfante |year=1983 |place=Manchester University Press|isbn= 9780719055409}}</ref>{{rp|100}}。}}

